NUMBER 45
NAME Morthain's Workshop
REGION 200
ASTRAL
FIXED_LIGHT
FORGE
*DESCRIPTION_START
This massive vaulted chamber is a study in organized chaos. The south wall
is covered with shelving containing metals of every type and quality. Along
the east wall is a rack containing hundreds of tools for working metals.
The west wall is dominated by a massive forge that seems to produce heat for
the coals with no apparent fuel source. The center of the room is devoted
entirely to work benches, covered with vises and clamps of all sizes. A disk
in the ceiling projects a shimmering energy beam on a silver platform in the
corner. The north wall contains three doors, a steel door marked 'Fayd', a
titanium door marked 'Kragenholm', and an alzyron door marked 'Private'.
*DESCRIPTION_END
