      ELSE
         GMMSG KMKTELEPORT location set to room #%0 and is in silent mode.
      ENDIF
   ENDIF
ENDIF

NUMBER 2700
NAME Citadel of the Crimson Band, Lobby
*DESCRIPTION_START
The floor of this hall is of dark flagstone, the walls of white marble
streaked with a deep red along which hang large, colorful tapestries. High
upon the walls, torches burn in ornate sconces casting a soft light into all
corners. Apprentices, off-duty guardsmen and couriers on official business
pass through this area intent on their business. A guard in plate armor,
bearing a crimson halberd stands stiffly at attention to one side of the
massive iron gate. A stone spiral staircase winds upward toward the turrets
above. An oak door is inset into the western wall along with a passage south.
*DESCRIPTION_END
