NUMBER 2702
NAME Crimson Band, Training Area
*DESCRIPTION_START
The smell of sweat and the clash of weaponry resounds through this chamber.
Here members of the Crimson Band hone their fighting skills under the watchful
eyes of instructors. Most activity takes place in the center of the room which
is kept clear of equipment to allow mock combat. The walls display the
weaponry of every race and culture from the heavy battle-axes favored by
Highlanders to the mysterious katana of the drakin. There is a door in the
northern wall.
