NUMBER 2703
NAME Crimson Band, Kitchen
*DESCRIPTION_START
The mouthwatering smell of freshly baked bread permeates the air. This area
is bustling with activity as cooks and apprentices scurry to and fro preparing
the Citadel's next meal. The immaculately clean pots, pans and other kitchen
utensils that fill the shelves are a testament to the strong willed chef,
Herimos Kushmen. A highlander and former fighter of some renown, he lost his
right arm during a battle and has since changed careers. Lining one corner of
the kitchen is a pantry stocked with all sorts of delicacies. A large cast
iron oven, the source of the delicious smell, sits in the center of the room.
A stairway to the storage cellar is visible in the east wall.
*DESCRIPTION_END
INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
