NUMBER 2707
NAME Crimson Band, NW Tower
*DESCRIPTION_START
This tower provides a sweeping view of the northwestern portion of Fayd,
including the tower of the Silver Arcana and the Royal Palace. Far to the
north, the peaks of the Teeth of Shartan are visible. To the west can be seen
the mighty Eltinmar river and the foreboding Grymwood forest. To one side is a
cauldron and a pile of melon sized stones which are clearly intended to deter
would-be invaders. You can see the street below over the edge of the wall, and
the ramparts continue on to the south and east.
