NAME Hallway of Warriors South
*DESCRIPTION_START
An ornate oriental rug covers the entire length of this baroque hallway. Muted
light flickers from silver leaf candleabras which are placed in such a way as
to allow future portraits to be hung here. A large tapestry hangs on the
southern wall covering it from floor to ceiling and flanked by two guardsmen.
