NUMBER 2715
NAME Crimson Band, Cyrano's Office
*DESCRIPTION_START
This is the office of Cyrano de Bergerac, current High Lord of the Crimson
Band. The floor is covered by a finely woven crimson and silver rug of Aelfen
weave. Near the center of the room is a large mirmach desk. Behind the desk
is a comfortable looking overstuffed crimson leather armchair. In the southwest
corner of the room stands a fearsome stuffed Kvantar warrior. In front of the
desk are two smaller oak chairs. Shelves line the western wall, displaying an
assortment of books and war mementos. A large painting in a black crystalline
frame of unknown origin hangs on the eastern wall. Beneath the painting is a
sofa with an ursine fur cover. The room is lit by ruby studded silver lanterns
situated to either side of a window located in the southern wall.
*DESCRIPTION_END
